HEADWORD: decolonize
<hw>decolonize</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>to release one's colonies and
free them to become independent nations; -- of nations.</def>
<altsp>[Also spelled <asp>decolonise</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
